                        Anthiyur,<br>
                        Erode.<br>
                        PIN - 638 501</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-left: 30px;" class="info-div">
                        <h2>About Us</h2>
                        <p>
                            <b>Founder:</b> K Sakthivel<br>
                            <b>CEO:</b> K Sakthivel<br>
                            <b>Products Admin:</b> K Sakthivel<br>
                            <b>Website Designer:</b> K Sakthivel<br>
